text: Khripunovsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Kuganaksky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Sterlitamak, 6 km from Bolshoy Kuganak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Khripunovsky
